data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated home in the desirable Bellair Golf Community! This 4-bedroom home is a delight, showcasing new vinyl and carpet throughout. Through the front door into the large foyer, you are greeted by French doors leading into a bright sitting room/study. The formal living room features a charming brick fireplace, adding warmth & character to the space. The heart of the home unfolds into an open concept, where the kitchen, dining area, and family room seamlessly blend together. The kitchen is a culinary haven with modern amenities and a stylish aesthetic. The hall guest bathroom has also been tastefully renovated. The master suite is a retreat in itself with a walk-in closet and a private patio entrance & master bath featuring a new glass walk-in shower & vanities Beyond the charms of the home, Bellair Golf Community provides numerous recreational amenities and hosts family-centered events, enhancing the sense of community and offering a vibrant lifestyle for residents. The convenience of being just minutes away from the new Phoenix Children's Hospital and Midwestern University adds to the appeal of this location. This home is not just a house, it's an opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and community. Don't miss the chance to make this your HOME and enjoy the best that Bellair has to offer!
